name: Cast4KODI
tagline: stripped Kodi fork, made by One Tech Genius. So far it has been released for for Android derivative for the Android Cell Phones And Tablets as their first platform
body: Cast4KODI is an open source for-profit media player / media center software that is a stripped Kodi fork, made by former XBMC developer One Tech Genius. So far it has been released for for Android derivative for the Android Cell Phones And Tablets as their first platform.
